<L>__{interior the treasury department day}
<A>__{in the grand lobby there are federal bank windows. schell is in line at one of these behind giles stuart, who completes a transaction and leaves, counting money. bilbo, barrelling the other way, intentionally slams into stuart, causing him to drop his money. bilbo and schell both kneel to help. schell places the open folio in stuart's hands. as the men pile his recovered money into the folio, stuart's puzzled, then intrigued. schell gives him a meaningful look.}
<B>__{close on a small wooden file box}
